ation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不爱我吗</span></span></p><p begin="28.366" end="31.018" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="28.366" end="28.580">I</span> <span begin="28.580" end="28.688">ain&apos;t</span> <span begin="28.688" end="28.813">a</span> <span begin="28.864" end="29.250">player,</span> <span begin="29.250" end="29.436">I</span> <span begin="29.436" end="29.572">just—</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不是花花公子 我只是</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="29.604" end="31.018"><span begin="29.604" end="29.972">(Player,</span> <span begin="29.972" end="30.137">I</span> <span begin="30.137" end="30.311">just,</span> <span begin="30.311" end="30.668">player,</span> <span begin="30.668" end="30.797">I</span> <span begin="30.797" end="31.018">just)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">花花公子 我只是 花花公子 我只是</span></span></p><p begin="31.043" end="33.077" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.043" end="31.228">You</span> <span begin="31.228" end="31.406">give</span> <span begin="31.406" end="31.598">me</span> <span begin="31.598" end="31.767">that</span> <span begin="31.767" end="32.300">kinda</span> <span begin="32.512" end="32.865">some</span><span begin="32.865" end="33.077">thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你给了我那种特别的感觉</span></p><p begin="33.236" end="36.119" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.236" end="33.452">Want</span> <span begin="33.452" end="33.639">it</span> <span begin="33.639" end="33.809">all</span> <span begin="33.809" end="33.953">the</span> <span begin="33.953" end="34.335">time,</span> <span begin="34.335" end="34.503">need</span> <span begin="34.503" end="34.693">it</span> <span begin="34.693" end="34.922">eve</span><span begin="34.922" end="35.049">ry</span><span begin="35.049" end="36.119">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每时每刻都想要 每天都需要</span></p><p begin="36.480" end="38.885" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.480" end="36.673">On</span> <span begin="36.673" end="36.810">a</span> <span begin="36.810" end="37.107">scale</span> <span begin="37.107" end="37.228">of</span> <span begin="37.228" end="37.413">one</span> <span begin="37.413" end="37.537">to</span> <span begin="37.583" end="37.778">ten,</span> <span begin="37.778" end="37.954">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="37.954" end="38.139">at</span> <span begin="38.139" end="38.323">a</span> <span begin="38.323" end="38.885">hundred</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">满分是十分 我就是一百分</span></p><p begin="39.027" end="41.478" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="39.027" end="39.415">Never</span> <span begin="39.415" end="39.622">get</span> <span begin="39.622" end="40.081">enough,</span> <span begin="40.127" end="40.303">I</span> <span begin="40.303" end="40.498">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="40.498" end="40.796">stay</span> <span begin="40.796" end="41.478">away</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永远都不会厌倦 我无法离开</span></p><p begin="42.332" end="45.512" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.332" end="42.441">If</span> <span begin="42.441" end="42.663">you</span> <span begin="42.663" end="42.895">want,</span> <span begin="42.895" end="43.098">well,</span> <span begin="43.098" end="43.208">I</span> <span begin="43.244" end="43.395">got</span> <span begin="43.395" end="43.588">it,</span> <span begin="43.588" end="43.746">I</span> <span begin="43.778" end="43.948">got</span> <span begin="43.948" end="44.097">it</span> <span begin="44.097" end="44.468">eve</span><span begin="44.513" end="44.877">ry</span><span begin="44.877" end="45.512">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只要你想要 好吧 我就满足你 我每天都能满足你</span></p><p begin="45.596" end="48.315" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.596" end="45.801">You</span> <span begin="45.801" end="45.945">can</span> <span begin="45.945" end="46.135">get</span> <span begin="46.135" end="46.529">what</span><span begin="46.529" end="46.663">e</span><span begin="46.663" end="46.889">ver</span> <span begin="46.889" end="47.054">you</span> <span begin="47.054" end="47.383">need</span> <span begin="47.404" end="47.764">from</span> <span begin="47.764" end="48.315">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你可以从我这里得到你需要的一切</span></p><p begin="48.503" end="50.644" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.503" end="48.694">Stay</span> <span begin="48.694" end="48.837">by</span> <span begin="48.837" end="49.021">your</span> <span begin="49.021" end="49.406">side,</span> <span begin="49.406" end="49.590">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="49.590" end="49.954">never</span> <span begin="49.954" end="50.307">leave</span> <span begin="50.307" end="50.644">ya</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">陪在你身边 我永远不会离开你</span></p><p begin="51.039" end="53.707" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="51.039" end="51.160">And</span> <span begin="51.160" end="51.280">I</span> <span begin="51.280" end="51.387">ain&apos;t</span> <span begin="51.407" end="51.775">going</span> <span begin="51.775" end="51.930">no</span><span begin="51.930" end="52.295">where</span> <span begin="52.322" end="52.476">&apos;cause</span> <span begin="52.476" end="52.683">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="52.683" end="52.831">a</span> <span begin="52.851" end="53.241">kee</span><span begin="53.241" end="53.707">per</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不会离开 因为你是我要守护的人</span></p><p begin="53.256" end="56.103" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.256" end="53.604">So,</span> <span begin="53.604" end="53.901">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="53.901" end="54.208">you</span> <span begin="54.208" end="55.368">wor</span><span begin="55.368" end="56.103">ry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以 不要担心</span></p><p begin="56.296" end="59.394" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.296" end="56.872">Baby,</span> <span begin="56.872" end="57.219">you</span> <span begin="57.291" end="58.